Package: MRdirection
Type: Package
Title: Runs the MRdirection function
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-01-06
Author: Sharon Lutz, Kirsten Voorhies
Maintainer: Sharon Lutz <smlutz@hsph.harvard.edu>
Description: The MRdirection package runs the MRdirection function which, using simulations, examines the causal direction returned by multiple MR approaches under different scenarios as specified by the user.
License: GPL-2